## ğŸ“˜ Introduction

**LSPoty** is a web application developed as part of the **Web Projects 2** course at **La Salle University**.  
The project was built using the **CodeIgniter** framework, inside **Docker** containers, and developed with the **PhpStorm** IDE.

LSPoty allows users to **search and play songs**, **discover artists and albums**, and **create or explore custom playlists**.  
It integrates with the **Jamendo API** to retrieve updated music information and includes user authentication, profile management, playlists, and full playback control.

